    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tools with serrated jaws, designed for gripping leather. In shoemaking hey are used for straining leather uppers over the last.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
